api_list.name: /propertyExtendedSearch (Extended search)
api_list.description:
Search for properties by parameters.
*Note.* If you search by exact address, the endpoint will return only zpid, or list of `zpid`s if it's a building with many units or `lotId`s for building.
**To get more information about a property by `zpid`, use a `/property` endpoint. For `lotId` use a `/building` endpoint.**
`location` is required if `polygon` and `coordinates` are empty.

about.description:
I'm happy to Facetime or Video a home if you're out of town or can't get there. Having grown up in Tampa, gone to school in St Petersburg and graduated from The University of Tampa (back when it was 2000 students) I'm very familiar with the history and neighborhoods of the area.   I have over 20 years experience in the Tampa Bay Market. I can show you houses or list your house in any area. I represent buyers, having made many, many deals, I know what to look for and pitfalls to avoid. Having sold may listings, I can help sell your home for the most money while helping to keep control of the sale.  I work with many mortgage brokers and title companies, inspectors and appraisers. I know what they are looking for. If I don't know a question, I know who to call. 

I know the ins and outs of real estate deals. If you're buying or selling, please call me and let's talk.  I work in Tampa, St Pete, Clearwater, Dunedin, Safety Harbor, Palm Harbor, Tarpon Springs, Sarasota, Riverview, Brandon, Seffner, Lakeland and Plant City.
   

When You're Thinking About Buying A Home

If all the houses you like are under contract, that means you just started looking or are not looking consistently. Don't give up. You may want to get on Zillow Alerts, so you're one of the first to know about new listings and we can go look and try to get it under contract the first day it's listed.

Every purchase or sale has bumps in the road. Don't take it personally. We will work with the seller or buyer and try to work out anything that comes up.

It is normal to offer and negotiate prices and terms on properties. Sometimes going back and forth many times. Sometimes verbally, sometimes texts, sometimes with written offers.

Esigns (Esignatures) are easy and convenient. In the old days, when I started, we had to print every page and meet the client to sign then initial any and every change. Now it's just a click of the mouse!

2 areas I specialize in are Ybor City.    It is 10 minutes to the $3billion project downtown. Construction has started on it with the owner of the Tampa Bay Lightnings money and Bill Gates. It is also 5 minutes from the new stadium that was on the front page of the paper but not for sure yet.  A great condo buy is in The Quarter in the heart of Ybor City, gated with a gated parking garage and 2 pools. It is walkable to famous 7th Ave. 

South Tampa - One of the most, if not the most prestigious areas in Tampa. South Tampa is on a peninsula and includes beautiful Bayshore Blvd. High ranking schools and Beautiful neighborhoods.   

I would like to email you explanations and the order of the buying process. I will include lists of phone numbers or mortgage brokers, inspectors, insurance agents, etc. 

Please call me and let's talk about your real estate wants and needs.

api_list.name: /resolveAddressToZpid (Resolving the addresses from the given file to zpid)
api_list.description:
Resolving the addresses from the given file to `zpid`.
The limit for the BASIC plan is 10 lines and for the other plans it is 100 lines.
***Cost: 1 request per line!*** Expand ==>
Code snippet (Python) [gist.github.com](https://gist.github.com/apimaker001/6ec89060307f8b5d15c0b245e378fbd4)

***How does this work?***
You send a file with the addresses (one per line) and as the answer will receive data, where you will find `jobNumber` field. After some time (1 line per 2 sec) use your `jobNumber` value and `/getJobResults` endpoint to get the results.

***Results example***
**You send the file with lines**
5500 Grand Lake Drive, San Antonio, TX
1636 Sonnet Drive, Grapevine, Texas 76051
2310 fairhill dr newport beach ca 92660

**You will receive the file with lines (format csv: address,zpid)**
"5500 Grand Lake Drive, San Antonio, TX",26187246
"1636 Sonnet Drive, Grapevine, Texas 76051",28959146
"2310 fairhill dr newport beach ca 92660",2069242807,25214848
